{"tid":716383,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世post]今年DSE考生/搵緊工嘅巴絲請入","createTime":"2018-06-25T08:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T14:06:51.000Z","uid":37971,"like":64,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5b6560d62e974ebf39db864ceb8a2bef3b465454","tid":716383,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:22:11.000Z","msg":"各位入咗嚟嘅巴絲，請先開咗呢個網，方便睇得明我講嘅嘢<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinesecommercialcode.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchinesecommercialcode.net%2F&d=2cyo8dFeyNMIOGkW81WWsp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b440da46\" target=\"_blank\">http://chinesecommercialcode.net/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你係今年DSE考生，近排收到呢兩個機構名嘅電話，請你唔好讀佢哋嘅top up degree課程：<br />\n3807 0108 2170 4958 2403 5148 0022 1800 /<br />\n5019 0948 6794 1648 2814 0588 2585<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n電話入面同你講嗰個課程嘅嘢，呢個post會提到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/26160/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/26160/1?ref=android</a><br />\n所以如果你聽過佢哋打嚟嘅電話，咁你就自己決定讀唔讀佢哋嘅課程啦<br />\n<br />\n至於搵緊工嘅朋友，都勸你唔好入呢間嘢做喇<br />\n但佢出recruitment唔係用呢個名<br />\n而係另一個：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkgoodjobs.com/job/part-time-sales-amp-marketing-officer/43296?show_emp=18705\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgoodjobs.com%2Fjob%2Fpart-time-sales-amp-marketing-officer%2F43296%3Fshow_emp%3D18705&d=2cyo8dFeyNMIOGkW81WWsp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=4d269023\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkgoodjobs.com/job/part-time-sales-amp-marketing-officer/43296?show_emp=18705</a><br />\n但依家係咪用呢個名我就唔知喇<br />\n如果你真係想入去做嘅<br />\n你可以睇咗呢個post先<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/217760/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/217760/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d19fe0967943ad1c39868bb39b3d606a2bfe1457","tid":716383,"uid":37971,"like":1,"disl